            <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Variables</b> tab of your Test Case.</li><li class="- topic/li ">Then click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Add</b>. A new row is added to the
            variable list.</li><li class="- topic/li ">Input variables.<note class="- topic/note "><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remember to save the test case once done.</p></li></ul></note><p class="- topic/p ">
